transcripts.text: I have the right to do whatever I want as president.  We're small business.  We can't even pay rent.  That's enough, right?  There's just so much chaos and so much disruption.  He is the president of chaos and disruption.  And on a scale of 1 to 10, how would you rate your response to this crisis?  I'd rate it a 10.  I think we've done a great job.
